title: Starlight (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor Swift just casually wrote a song about her boyfriend's grandparents! Was this the beginning of her storytelling songwriting? She was inspired by a photograph to write this beautiful song!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
